<h3>PUT /api/users/update_profile</h3>
<div>
  update profile of current user
</div>
<b>Resource URL </b>
<div>
  http://localhost:3000/api/users/update_profile
</div>
<b>Example request</b>
<div>
  curl -XPUT -H 'Authorization: Bearer auth_token' --data "user[full_name]=Tran" "http://localhost:3000/api/users/update_profile"
  <br/>
  auth_token: jwt token of current user
</div>
